N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 601.2 - Application of part

State Regulations

This Part shall apply to apprenticeship programs and
agreements covered by article 23 of the Labor Law, including programs and
agreements relating to public work projects as defined by Federal and State
labor laws, and to privately financed activities. Notes
